{{medical}}{{Infobox brain|Name=顶上小叶|Latin=lobulus parietalis superior|Image=Gray726 superior parietal lobule.png|Caption=左侧大脑半球（顶上小叶位于橙色标记处）|IsPartOf=|Components=|Artery=|Vein=}}'''顶上小叶'''（英文：Superior parietal lobule）位于[[大脑|大脑]][[顶叶|顶叶]]，前方有[[中央后沟|中央后沟]]将其与[[中央后回|中央后回]]隔开，但在后沟终端处时常与后回有连接<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=Superior Parietal Lobule - an overview|url=https://www.sciencedirect.com/topics/neuroscience/superior-parietal-lobule|accessdate=2021-04-11|work=|publisher=ScienceDirect|language=en}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=顶上小叶|url=https://www.imaios.com/cn/e-Anatomy/node_322323/2743|accessdate=2021-04-11|work=IMAIOS|language=cn}}</ref>。顶上小叶包含[[布罗德曼分区系统|布罗德卡分区]]第5、第7区<ref name=":0" />。顶上小叶在[[大脑半球|大脑半球]]的内侧面形成[[楔前叶|楔前叶]]<ref name=":1">{{Cite web|title=Superior parietal lobule|url=https://radiopaedia.org/articles/superior-parietal-lobule?lang=us|accessdate=2021-04-11|last=Gai|first=Dayu|work=|publisher=Radiopaedia|language=en-US}}</ref>。

== 结构 ==
顶上小叶后方是[[顶枕沟|顶枕沟]]的外侧部分，与[[枕叶|枕叶]]相隔。下方与[[顶下小叶|顶下小叶]]之间由[[顶内沟|顶内沟]]的水平部分隔开<ref name=":1" />。

顶上小叶还与许多主要[[白质|白质]][[神经通路|神经通路]]相连，譬如[[扣带回|扣带回]]中的白质通路和{{le|上纵束|Superior longitudinal fasciculus}}<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Cerebral White Matter|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC3753195/|last=Schmahmann|first=Jeremy D.|last2=Smith|first2=Eric E.|date=2008-10|journal=Annals of the New York Academy of Sciences|doi=10.1196/annals.1444.017|volume=1142|pages=266–309|issn=0077-8923|pmc=3753195|pmid=18990132|last3=Eichler|first3=Florian S.|last4=Filley|first4=Christopher M.}}</ref>。

== 功能 ==
顶上小叶与大脑空间定向功能有关，可记住物体在空间的位置<ref name=":0" />。在[[工作记忆|工作记忆]]的信息操控和重置中扮演重要角色<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Superior Parietal Cortex Is Critical for the Manipulation of Information in Working Memory|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC2799248/|last=Koenigs|first=Michael|last2=Barbey|first2=Aron K.|date=2009-11-25|journal=The Journal of Neuroscience|issue=47|doi=10.1523/JNEUROSCI.3706-09.2009|volume=29|pages=14980–14986|issn=0270-6474|pmc=2799248|pmid=19940193|last3=Postle|first3=Bradley R.|last4=Grafman|first4=Jordan}}</ref>。

此外，顶上小叶接受大量视觉信息和手部的感觉信息，可形成对物体形状、粗糙程度、大小、材质等的感觉<ref name=":0" />。

== 临床 ==
[[大脑半球|大脑半球]]一侧的顶上小叶受损，可导致身体另一侧的触觉或立体觉[[失认症|失认症]]，或[[半侧空间忽略症|半侧空间忽略症]]<ref>{{Cite book|chapter=Astereognosis|title=StatPearls|url=http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/books/NBK560773/|publisher=StatPearls Publishing|date=2021|location=Treasure Island (FL)|pmid=32809608|first=Ajaya Kumar A.|last=Unnithan|first2=Prabhu D.|last2=Emmady}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|title=Analysis of lesions in patients with unilateral tactile agnosia using cytoarchitectonic probabilistic maps|url=https://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/abs/10.1002/hbm.20617|last=Hömke|first=Lars|last2=Amunts|first2=Katrin|date=2009|journal=Human Brain Mapping|issue=5|doi=10.1002/hbm.20617|volume=30|pages=1444–1456|language=en|issn=1097-0193|pmc=PMC6870829|pmid=18636551|last3=Bönig|first3=Lutz|last4=Fretz|first4=Christian|last5=Binkofski|first5=Ferdinand|last6=Zilles|first6=Karl|last7=Weder|first7=Bruno}}</ref>。

